      "text": "## References\n\nDuncan, Elmer H. 1980. “The Philosophy of Stephen C. Pepper: An Appraisal.” _Paunch_ 53: 63. https://web.archive.org/web/20070523221046/http://people.sunyit.edu/~harrell/Pepper/pep_duncan.htm.\n\nPepper, Stephen C. 1942. “Preface.” In _World Hypotheses: A Study in Evidence_, vii–ix. Berkeley: University of California Press. https://doi.org/10.1525/9780520341869."
